## ğŸ”— API Integration

Frontend connects to FastAPI backend:
- `GET /api/frames` - Get frame series
- `POST /api/drawings/generate` - Generate drawing
- `GET /api/projects` - List projects
- `POST /api/export/pdf` - Export to PDF
